    "teacher_markdown": "💡 **Teacher Tip**: Don't let students overcomplicate this level - they should be using this as practice for understanding how function calls and definitions are used. Dragging-and-dropping into the correct section is all they need to do!\r\n\r\n**Rubrics & Feedback:** Assessment levels have rubrics where you can provide feedback to students. Use the TA icon to open the evaluation tool and give feedback to students. [Learn more by watching this video overview](https://www.loom.com/share/9e86438769e940afbafa9efc602a12e3).",
